# 💱 Currency Convertor Web App

This is a simple **Currency Convertor** web application built using Python and Flask (or Streamlit).

It allows users to convert currency from one to another (e.g., USD to INR) using a fixed or live exchange rate.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Real-time currency conversion (can be connected to an API)
- Clean UI with input fields
- Fast and responsive
- Easy to deploy on the web (Render/Replit)

